---
import Separator from "../../unitComponents/Separator.astro";
import Boxes from "../../../assets/images/Boxes.webp";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
---

<section
  class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-8 md:px-52 mt-20"
>
  <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-end max-w-7xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-grisT">SPARE PARTS</h1>
    <div>
      <Separator />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-10 font-bold max-w-7xl">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
      Triaso spare parts are precisely engineered to deliver optimal
      performance, extending both component lifespan and overall equipment
      durability. With unmatched quality and reliability, they help maintain
      peak efficiency while minimizing downtime. <br />
      We understand the importance of keeping your equipment running non-stop. The
      operation of many other machines depends on the reliability of your asphalt
      plant. <br />
      Strict quality control ensures the operation of your asphalt plant with low
      maintenance for many years.
    </p>
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
      <img src={Boxes.src} alt="" class="w-3/4 rounded-2xl" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
